\begin_layout Standard
The Service Location Protocol (SLP) is an IETF standard published in 1997.
 It has since been superseeded by version 2 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Guttman1999"

\end_inset

.
 Since its publication, it has seen wide adoption ranging from embedded
 devices up the enterprise scale applications.
 This paper will be based on SLPv2, though most of this paper possibly also
 applies to SLPv1.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Protocols basics
