\begin_layout Standard
Regarding security, SLP provides only pre-established trust relationships
 based on asymmetric keying.
 This allows for DAs, SAa and UAs to authentication each other.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

On top of that asymmetric keying allows to verify message integrity by all
 parties.
 The built-in algorithm is Digital Signature Algorithm (DSA) 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
